===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# [[Goidelic]]; any [[Goidelic]] language.
## [[Irish Gaelic]].
## [[Manx Gaelic]].
## [[Scottish Gaelic]].

====Usage notes====
When used without any modifier, ''Gaelic'' refers most often to Scottish Gaelic. Irish Gaelic and Manx Gaelic are more commonly called simply {{m|en|Irish}} and {{m|en|Manx}}.

